=============================================================================
CRITICAL INFRASTRUCTURE DISCLAIMER & ANNEX
=============================================================================

1. SYSTEM LOCKOUT & DOWNTIME WARNING:
This automation suite modifies critical low-level kernel parameters, operating
system network configurations, configurations of the systemd-ssh-generator, 
and firewall routing matrices. Improper scheduling or out-of-order execution 
of these playbooks against live environments WILL cause immediate infrastructure 
lockouts, unrecoverable SSH drops, and server downtime.

2. MANDATORY RECOVERY PREPARATION:
Before executing any targets provided within this repository (including but not 
limited to 'make production-harden' or 'make production-bootstrap') against a 
live Virtual Private Server (VPS) or bare-metal node, the operator is STRICTLY 
REQUIRED to perform a full system state snapshot or image backup via their 
infrastructure provider's control panel (e.g., Contabo, Hetzner, DigitalOcean).

3. NO LIABILITY ACCEPTANCE:
The author maintains absolute zero liability for any broken production nodes, 
lost data, compromised system access, or commercial damages arising from the 
utilization of this automation framework. You execute these orchestration 
routines entirely at your own risk.